item.title: About
item.description: I am a mathematics teacher at Cegep Gérald-Godin in Montreal. I have a bachelor’s degree in mathematics from Université Laval as well as a master’s degree in mathematics from Université de Montréal. I’ve been teaching at the college level since 2012 and full time since 2015.
